'''Area Defense Anti-Munitions''' ('''ADAM''') is an experimental short range ground-to-air [[anti-missile]] weapons system being developed by [[Lockheed Martin]]. It uses a 10 kW fiber laser to attack its targets.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-11386_3-57583531-76/lockheed-laser-weapon-hits-its-mark-again/|title=Lockheed laser weapon hits its mark again|author=Johnathan Skillings|publisher=CNET|date= May 8, 2013|accessdate=2013-05-09}}</ref><ref>http://www.lockheedmartin.com/us/news/press-releases/2014/may/0507-ss-adam.html</ref>

